org.springframework.boot.actuate.endpoint.web

类 WebEndpointResponse<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.springframework.boot.actuate.endpoint.web.WebEndpointResponse<T>
  • 类型参数:
    T - the type of the response body

    public final class WebEndpointResponse<T>
extends Object
    A WebEndpointResponse can be returned by an operation on a WebEndpointExtension to provide additional, web-specific information such as the HTTP status code.
    从以下版本开始:
    2.0.0
    作者:
    Stephane Nicoll, Andy Wilkinson, Vedran Pavic
